**Credit card EMI conversion** lets you convert large purchases into monthly instalments. Standard credit card EMIs charge 13–24% p.a. interest, though some merchants offer 'no-cost EMI' where the interest is subsidised. This calculator helps you compute the true cost of credit card EMIs, including the effective annual rate and total interest outflow.
